WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 11=

00:02:05.060 --> 00:02:07.700 line:80%
Looks like Master You
can't clear your name this time.

00:02:10.930 --> 00:02:13.370 line:80%
My foster father devoted himself
to bringing the Mu Clan

00:02:13.810 --> 00:02:14.780 line:80%
back to the Li Sect.

00:02:14.830 --> 00:02:16.060 line:80%
He'd die for it without regret.

00:02:16.060 --> 00:02:16.900 line:80%
I have been shaped by

00:02:17.210 --> 00:02:19.020 line:80%
my foster father's words
since childhood.

00:02:19.020 --> 00:02:21.020 line:80%
Always place the Mu Clan above all else.

00:02:21.150 --> 00:02:22.070 line:80%
After my foster father

00:02:22.070 --> 00:02:23.780 line:80%
was betrayed by that traitor Nie Zhe,

00:02:24.210 --> 00:02:25.810 line:80%
I endured humiliation and hardship,

00:02:25.810 --> 00:02:26.780 line:80%
and tangled with scum like

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:28.140 line:80%
Yu Huiyin and Xiong Qianjin.

00:02:28.780 --> 00:02:31.020 line:80%
All to wait for Mr. Mu's return.

00:02:31.580 --> 00:02:32.490 line:80%
Unexpectedly,

00:02:32.490 --> 00:02:33.690 line:80%
heaven is just,

00:02:33.930 --> 00:02:35.250 line:80%
and Mr. Mu, you're safe and sound.

00:02:37.180 --> 00:02:38.060 line:80%
Now foster father

00:02:39.180 --> 00:02:41.250 line:80%
can finally rest in peace.

00:02:42.780 --> 00:02:43.970 line:80%
Last night, I heard

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:47.020 line:80%
someone threw
Elder Qiu's memorial tablet

00:02:47.900 --> 00:02:49.210 line:80%
off the cliff.

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:53.460 line:80%
It must be that scoundrel Li Yi's doing.

00:02:53.460 --> 00:02:54.340 line:80%
I never thought,

00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:55.970 line:80%
he'd commit such a despicable,

00:02:55.970 --> 00:02:57.120 line:80%
unforgivable act.

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:58.020 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:02:58.020 --> 00:02:59.210 line:80%
you should've killed him right then.

00:02:59.410 --> 00:03:00.340 line:80%
Torn him limb from limb.

00:03:13.810 --> 00:03:14.650 line:80%
Enough.

00:03:15.140 --> 00:03:15.980 line:80%
Get up.

00:03:17.490 --> 00:03:18.620 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:03:18.620 --> 00:03:19.460 line:80%
You Guanyue,

00:03:19.600 --> 00:03:21.930 line:80%
you know the last person
who came within three steps of me?

00:03:22.300 --> 00:03:24.180 line:80%
Their grave's already overgrown.

00:03:26.690 --> 00:03:29.020 line:80%
I'm utterly loyal to you, Mr. Mu.

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:30.580 line:80%
Heaven and Earth can bear witness.

00:03:31.370 --> 00:03:33.060 line:80%
If you have any use for me,

00:03:33.300 --> 00:03:34.140 line:80%
I will surely

00:03:34.140 --> 00:03:35.370 line:80%
serve you with all my heart,

00:03:35.810 --> 00:03:37.900 line:80%
even unto death.

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:38.740 line:80%
Very well.

00:03:39.860 --> 00:03:40.900 line:80%
Then I'll be counting on

00:03:41.180 --> 00:03:43.900 line:80%
your talents from now on, Mr. You.

00:03:50.460 --> 00:03:51.300 line:80%
Have some tea.

00:04:14.090 --> 00:04:15.250 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Mu.

00:04:24.970 --> 00:04:26.820 line:80%
I've called you all here tonight

00:04:27.020 --> 00:04:29.340 line:80%
because calamity looms,
and my future grows uncertain.

00:04:29.700 --> 00:04:31.020 line:80%
I know you're all loyal,

00:04:31.260 --> 00:04:32.650 line:80%
but I can't bear to
drag you down with me.

00:04:32.820 --> 00:04:33.700 line:80%
After much thought,

00:04:33.850 --> 00:04:35.410 line:80%
I've decided to divide all my savings

00:04:35.410 --> 00:04:36.970 line:80%
among every single one of you.

00:04:37.170 --> 00:04:38.140 line:80%
Take care, everyone.

00:04:38.850 --> 00:04:40.780 line:80%
Master You, what's happening?

00:04:41.050 --> 00:04:43.340 line:80%
Chief failed to ambush
the Six Sects of Beichen

00:04:43.780 --> 00:04:44.850 line:80%
and fled in defeat.

00:04:45.050 --> 00:04:46.170 line:80%
In a fury and shame,

00:04:46.170 --> 00:04:47.010 line:80%
he actually...

00:04:47.500 --> 00:04:49.650 line:80%
He ordered every altar to
capture innocent villagers

00:04:49.650 --> 00:04:51.290 line:80%
to refine corpse slaves.

00:04:51.290 --> 00:04:52.850 line:80%
- What?
- Corpse slaves?

00:04:53.500 --> 00:04:55.410 line:80%
The art of refining a corpse slave

00:04:56.260 --> 00:04:57.460 line:80%
is utterly vicious.

00:04:57.650 --> 00:04:58.850 line:80%
If he dares do this,

00:04:59.260 --> 00:05:01.940 line:80%
I'm afraid Heaven itself
will strike us down.

00:05:01.940 --> 00:05:04.290 line:80%
Besides, if corpse slaves
return to the world,

00:05:04.290 --> 00:05:06.900 line:80%
all Jianghu sects
will rise up against us.

00:05:07.170 --> 00:05:08.050 line:80%
By then,

00:05:08.500 --> 00:05:11.380 line:80%
there will surely be another bloodbath.

00:05:12.090 --> 00:05:14.730 line:80%
I can't bear to let my brothers
die with me.

00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:17.530 line:80%
After you take this gold and silver,

00:05:18.140 --> 00:05:19.700 line:80%
just make your plans for the future.

00:05:20.140 --> 00:05:20.980 line:80%
Plans?

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:22.940 line:80%
We, the old followers of Elder Qiu,

00:05:23.070 --> 00:05:24.780 line:80%
have long been a thorn
in the Chief's side.

00:05:24.900 --> 00:05:25.970 line:80%
If we're attacked,

00:05:26.140 --> 00:05:27.020 line:80%
we'll be the first

00:05:27.020 --> 00:05:28.260 line:80%
to be thrown to the wolves.

00:05:28.410 --> 00:05:29.250 line:80%
Years ago,

00:05:29.380 --> 00:05:30.900 line:80%
the former Chief Nie Hengcheng

00:05:31.410 --> 00:05:32.610 line:80%
refined these corpse slaves

00:05:33.500 --> 00:05:35.140 line:80%
and throw everyone into panic.

00:05:35.140 --> 00:05:36.380 line:80%
Half the sect are casualties.

00:05:37.380 --> 00:05:38.220 line:80%
And now,

00:05:38.650 --> 00:05:40.290 line:80%
are we doomed to
repeat the same mistake?

00:05:41.650 --> 00:05:43.780 line:80%
Those corpse slaves, that unnatural filth,

00:05:44.050 --> 00:05:46.290 line:80%
were the Nie clan's doing
to eliminate their enemies.

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:48.650 line:80%
Sadly, none within the sect
could restrain the Nie clan.

00:05:49.060 --> 00:05:50.090 line:80%
If Mr. Mu were still here...

00:05:50.090 --> 00:05:51.260 line:80%
If Mr. Mu were alive,

00:05:51.260 --> 00:05:52.850 line:80%
he'd never let the Chief
run amok like this!

00:05:53.610 --> 00:05:54.700 line:80%
Don't call him Chief.

00:05:55.050 --> 00:05:55.940 line:80%
That whole family

00:05:56.090 --> 00:05:58.090 line:80%
are traitors who stole
the Mu clan's legacy!

00:05:58.090 --> 00:06:00.610 line:80%
It's a pity Mr. Mu vanished long ago.

00:06:00.900 --> 00:06:04.140 line:80%
Seems you all still hold
the Mu clan in high regard.

00:06:04.850 --> 00:06:05.690 line:80%
If

00:06:06.700 --> 00:06:08.460 line:80%
the Young Master returns safely,

00:06:09.380 --> 00:06:10.500 line:80%
what will you do?

00:06:14.990 --> 00:06:16.500 line:80%
You Guanyue,
Master of Qinglong Altar,

00:06:16.650 --> 00:06:18.380 line:80%
bows to welcome Mr. Mu's return.

00:06:29.850 --> 00:06:30.730 line:80%
W... What?

00:06:36.090 --> 00:06:36.930 line:80%
Young Master.

00:06:37.420 --> 00:06:38.300 line:80%
The Founder of Mu clan

00:06:39.090 --> 00:06:40.090 line:80%
founded the Li Sect

00:06:40.550 --> 00:06:42.090 line:80%
to detach from worldly affairs

00:06:42.650 --> 00:06:44.700 line:80%
and have disciples aid one another

00:06:45.850 --> 00:06:47.090 line:80%
and share honor and disgrace.

00:06:48.090 --> 00:06:49.290 line:80%
But now, Nie Zhe

00:06:49.700 --> 00:06:51.020 line:80%
acts against all principles.

00:06:51.140 --> 00:06:52.340 line:80%
He's cruel and without virtue,

00:06:53.220 --> 00:06:54.730 line:80%
ignoring the lives of fellow disciples

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:57.170 line:80%
and throwing the Li Sect into trouble.

00:06:58.090 --> 00:06:58.930 line:80%
The Mu clan

00:07:00.530 --> 00:07:01.730 line:80%
will never stand by!

00:07:03.940 --> 00:07:05.650 line:80%
Those who do not wish to follow Mr. Mu

00:07:05.900 --> 00:07:07.530 line:80%
may take the gold and leave on your own.

00:07:07.630 --> 00:07:09.020 line:80%
Mr. Mu will not hold it against you.

00:07:11.090 --> 00:07:12.050 line:80%
Th... this…

00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:20.340 line:80%
My foster father's
death anniversary is near.

00:07:20.610 --> 00:07:23.500 line:80%
Looks like Nie Zhe
is about to start another purge.

00:07:32.460 --> 00:07:34.610 line:80%
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

00:07:35.940 --> 00:07:38.340 line:80%
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

00:07:38.650 --> 00:07:41.050 line:80%
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

00:07:41.340 --> 00:07:43.610 line:80%
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

00:07:44.090 --> 00:07:46.500 line:80%
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

00:07:46.780 --> 00:07:49.410 line:80%
Wipe out the traitor Nie
and restore the Mu clan!

00:07:53.140 --> 00:07:54.580 line:80%
He surrendered that fast?

00:07:56.340 --> 00:07:57.610 line:80%
Looks like Mu Qingyan

00:07:58.140 --> 00:08:00.050 line:80%
truly has some clever tactics.

00:08:03.850 --> 00:08:06.140 line:80%
Seize that girl named Xing.

00:08:06.340 --> 00:08:08.090 line:80%
I'll have big use for her soon.

00:08:09.140 --> 00:08:09.980 line:80%
Yes.

00:08:15.820 --> 00:08:18.020 line:80%
You Guanyue has always been
a smooth operator,

00:08:18.170 --> 00:08:19.820 line:80%
currying favor with everyone.

00:08:21.020 --> 00:08:22.850 line:80%
His surrender isn't surprising.

00:08:23.580 --> 00:08:24.700 line:80%
But why would the others

00:08:25.210 --> 00:08:26.610 line:80%
throw their lives away?

00:08:26.610 --> 00:08:27.460 line:80%
Fengge.

00:08:30.500 --> 00:08:32.810 line:80%
What do you think of Mu Qingyan?

00:08:33.570 --> 00:08:34.740 line:80%
I can't see through him.

00:08:35.140 --> 00:08:36.490 line:80%
When Mu Zhengming was still alive,

00:08:36.490 --> 00:08:37.410 line:80%
he was just a young man.

00:08:37.830 --> 00:08:39.650 line:80%
Every day he only read books
and grew flowers,

00:08:40.100 --> 00:08:41.450 line:80%
seeming gentle and harmless.

00:08:41.780 --> 00:08:43.050 line:80%
But after Mu Zhengming's death,

00:08:43.690 --> 00:08:45.620 line:80%
he quickly rallied Elder Qiu's faction,

00:08:45.760 --> 00:08:46.810 line:80%
stormed the Bliss Palace.

00:08:47.380 --> 00:08:48.450 line:80%
He nearly killed the Chief.

00:08:51.140 --> 00:08:53.330 line:80%
That was just over a year ago.

00:08:55.050 --> 00:08:55.890 line:80%
Anyone

00:08:56.450 --> 00:08:58.260 line:80%
who endured what he did

00:08:58.450 --> 00:09:00.100 line:80%
would have fallen into the abyss.

00:09:00.380 --> 00:09:02.620 line:80%
But he clawed his way out of hell.

00:09:04.220 --> 00:09:05.260 line:80%
It proves

00:09:05.930 --> 00:09:07.690 line:80%
he has something to rely on.

00:09:07.690 --> 00:09:09.100 line:80%
I don't care what he's relying on.

00:09:09.450 --> 00:09:10.410 line:80%
Like I said,

00:09:10.900 --> 00:09:11.780 line:80%
if he comes,

00:09:11.900 --> 00:09:12.860 line:80%
he dies.

00:09:22.590 --> 00:09:24.220 line:80%
They've already taken
the Qinglong Altar.

00:09:25.930 --> 00:09:26.980 line:80%
Never thought

00:09:27.690 --> 00:09:29.690 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is actually pretty capable.

00:09:30.100 --> 00:09:31.410 line:80%
Nie Zhe is such a useless fool.

00:09:31.780 --> 00:09:33.530 line:80%
Honestly, that's not so bad.

00:09:33.650 --> 00:09:35.260 line:80%
The two sides fight nonstop,

00:09:35.260 --> 00:09:36.380 line:80%
draining each other dry,

00:09:36.380 --> 00:09:37.450 line:80%
losing everything.

00:09:37.690 --> 00:09:38.530 line:80%
Perfect.

00:09:38.780 --> 00:09:39.620 line:80%
Dad.

00:09:40.780 --> 00:09:41.650 line:80%
Right now

00:09:41.650 --> 00:09:43.020 line:80%
the demon sect is tearing itself apart.

00:09:43.140 --> 00:09:45.570 line:80%
Why don't we sneak into
the Hanhai Mountains

00:09:45.570 --> 00:09:46.900 line:80%
and wipe them out in one fell swoop?

00:09:54.820 --> 00:09:55.740 line:80%
Lingbo, you're valiant.

00:09:56.740 --> 00:09:57.580 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:09:58.620 --> 00:09:59.530 line:80%
Master.

00:09:59.540 --> 00:10:00.860 line:80%
What's your take on this?

00:10:01.540 --> 00:10:03.450 line:80%
The Nie clan has held the demon sect
for decades.

00:10:04.830 --> 00:10:06.860 line:80%
Nie Zhe is backed by
Nie Hengcheng's old followers.

00:10:06.860 --> 00:10:07.700 line:80%
His foundation is solid.

00:10:07.900 --> 00:10:09.780 line:80%
Mu Qingyan may have seized
the Qinglong Altar,

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:12.330 line:80%
but the scale of their internal strife
remains unknown.

00:10:12.740 --> 00:10:14.100 line:80%
Until we get definite news,

00:10:14.930 --> 00:10:15.780 line:80%
I think

00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:17.500 line:80%
we should not act rashly.

00:10:17.740 --> 00:10:18.980 line:80%
That makes sense.

00:10:20.570 --> 00:10:21.570 line:80%
The Qinglong Altar,

00:10:21.810 --> 00:10:23.330 line:80%
though the gateway of the demon sect,

00:10:23.930 --> 00:10:26.410 line:80%
is weak in strength
and cannot stand alone.

00:10:26.410 --> 00:10:28.260 line:80%
If Nie Zhe strikes with
overwhelming force,

00:10:28.780 --> 00:10:29.620 line:80%
the Mu clan

00:10:29.980 --> 00:10:31.380 line:80%
will likely be wiped out.

00:10:31.740 --> 00:10:32.580 line:80%
And you guys

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:34.780 line:80%
don't just focus on
martial training all day.

00:10:35.260 --> 00:10:38.170 line:80%
Take some time to
read more books like Yuzhi.

00:10:40.530 --> 00:10:41.370 line:80%
Zhao,

00:10:43.410 --> 00:10:44.690 line:80%
come walk with me.

00:10:57.450 --> 00:10:58.290 line:80%
Zhao.

00:10:58.980 --> 00:11:01.260 line:80%
I promised your aunt

00:11:01.690 --> 00:11:03.050 line:80%
that as long as I live,

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:04.980 line:80%
I will keep you safe.

00:11:05.450 --> 00:11:07.780 line:80%
This time, I was trapped by a villain,

00:11:08.540 --> 00:11:10.860 line:80%
leaving you to go down
the mountain alone to find medicine.

00:11:11.410 --> 00:11:12.250 line:80%
I have

00:11:12.930 --> 00:11:14.290 line:80%
failed your aunt.

00:11:16.220 --> 00:11:17.810 line:80%
She would never be angry with you.

00:11:18.380 --> 00:11:19.860 line:80%
You are her closest

00:11:19.860 --> 00:11:20.810 line:80%
and most trusted.

00:11:21.100 --> 00:11:23.100 line:80%
Closer than Uncle Zhou,
closer than my parents.

00:11:23.100 --> 00:11:24.570 line:80%
Your bond is steadfast, like kin.

00:11:24.980 --> 00:11:26.380 line:80%
Mom's always been jealous of it.

00:11:28.410 --> 00:11:29.260 line:80%
Besides,

00:11:29.980 --> 00:11:32.100 line:80%
if Master hadn't gone to
Luoying Valley every year

00:11:32.100 --> 00:11:33.450 line:80%
to heal her and sustain her life,

00:11:33.450 --> 00:11:34.330 line:80%
wasting your inner power,

00:11:35.830 --> 00:11:37.860 line:80%
how could you have been tricked
by villains so easily?

00:11:41.100 --> 00:11:42.450 line:80%
What's the use of going every year?

00:11:43.410 --> 00:11:44.250 line:80%
Your aunt...

00:11:45.220 --> 00:11:46.740 line:80%
still left in the end.

00:11:50.780 --> 00:11:52.050 line:80%
Master.

00:11:53.140 --> 00:11:54.570 line:80%
Have you forgotten what aunt said?

00:11:54.980 --> 00:11:56.290 line:80%
People come and go.

00:11:56.290 --> 00:11:57.450 line:80%
It's all fate.

00:11:58.050 --> 00:11:59.050 line:80%
No need to grieve.

00:12:00.410 --> 00:12:01.380 line:80%
I understand.

00:12:02.930 --> 00:12:04.740 line:80%
There's something I must ask you.

00:12:05.020 --> 00:12:05.920 line:80%
About Chang Ning.

00:12:05.930 --> 00:12:06.930 line:80%
Do you know where he went?

00:12:10.220 --> 00:12:11.650 line:80%
He said he's tired of Jianghu,

00:12:11.950 --> 00:12:13.330 line:80%
and retired to live as a wealthy man.

00:12:16.530 --> 00:12:17.370 line:80%
Zhao,

00:12:17.570 --> 00:12:18.410 line:80%
you're

00:12:18.780 --> 00:12:19.930 line:80%
pure-hearted,

00:12:19.950 --> 00:12:21.050 line:80%
and loyal to your loved ones.

00:12:21.050 --> 00:12:22.380 line:80%
I don't oppose that,

00:12:22.930 --> 00:12:24.860 line:80%
but the heart of man is unfathomable.

00:12:24.860 --> 00:12:26.020 line:80%
It's hard to tell friend from foe.

00:12:26.650 --> 00:12:27.490 line:80%
From now on,

00:12:27.590 --> 00:12:29.450 line:80%
you must not leave the sect
without permission.

00:12:29.450 --> 00:12:31.100 line:80%
Don't make your parents worry about you.

00:12:35.050 --> 00:12:35.890 line:80%
And,

00:12:36.620 --> 00:12:37.900 line:80%
don't mind I'm nagging.

00:12:38.930 --> 00:12:40.170 line:80%
I'm just scared

00:12:41.330 --> 00:12:43.410 line:80%
I can't protect you.

00:12:43.860 --> 00:12:45.330 line:80%
Scared you'll end up like your aunt,

00:12:45.860 --> 00:12:47.380 line:80%
stubborn and gone forever.

00:12:50.450 --> 00:12:51.930 line:80%
The struggle has lasted for 100 years,

00:12:52.380 --> 00:12:53.690 line:80%
causing countless blood feuds.

00:12:53.980 --> 00:12:55.500 line:80%
One wrong step

00:12:56.170 --> 00:12:58.050 line:80%
can lead to eternal damnation.

00:12:58.500 --> 00:12:59.340 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:13:01.900 --> 00:13:02.740 line:80%
I do.

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:05.340 line:80%
Come.

00:13:34.650 --> 00:13:37.330 line:80%
Has Master guessed
Chang Ning's identity?

00:13:41.780 --> 00:13:43.530 line:80%
Fine, I won't meddle.

00:13:43.740 --> 00:13:44.580 line:80%
I'm busy right now.

00:13:45.530 --> 00:13:47.500 line:80%
My Golden Silk Armor is launching soon.

00:13:47.980 --> 00:13:49.140 line:80%
I have to manage the shops

00:13:50.050 --> 00:13:51.290 line:80%
and contact buyers.

00:14:05.050 --> 00:14:05.890 line:80%
(Zhao.)

00:14:06.020 --> 00:14:07.410 line:80%
(Have you been well?)

00:14:07.650 --> 00:14:08.810 line:80%
(Dad came back and said)

00:14:09.020 --> 00:14:10.330 line:80%
(Ning has left.)

00:14:10.620 --> 00:14:12.220 line:80%
(Where did he go?)

00:14:12.500 --> 00:14:13.780 line:80%
(I'm so worried about him.)

00:14:14.100 --> 00:14:15.330 line:80%
(How is his wound now?)

00:14:15.690 --> 00:14:18.220 line:80%
(I only eat vegetarian food
at Grandma's home.)

00:14:18.380 --> 00:14:20.500 line:80%
(I feel like I'm turning into a sheep.)

00:14:20.810 --> 00:14:23.690 line:80%
(I really crave Ning's wontons.)

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:25.570 line:80%
(The taste still lingers on my lips.)

00:14:26.020 --> 00:14:28.260 line:80%
(My mouth is watering.)

00:14:28.570 --> 00:14:32.410 line:80%
(Where else can I find wontons
that delicious?)

00:14:32.620 --> 00:14:35.290 line:80%
(I should have made him
write down the recipe.)

00:14:37.420 --> 00:14:42.410 line:80%
♪You come to my dreams again♪

00:14:43.740 --> 00:14:49.770 line:80%
♪On this cold day, drunk with wine♪

00:14:51.740 --> 00:14:58.490 line:80%
♪Life shifts, a thousand faces pass by♪

00:14:59.100 --> 00:15:04.650 line:80%
♪Yet I never forget yours♪

00:15:06.270 --> 00:15:11.920 line:80%
♪Beneath the stars,
I await the rising sun♪

00:15:12.560 --> 00:15:19.530 line:80%
♪Across rivers and mountains,
I roam free and wide♪

00:15:20.430 --> 00:15:27.280 line:80%
♪All the youth and bliss simply
could be boiled down to a toast♪

00:15:27.800 --> 00:15:32.550 line:80%
♪Ten years of turmoil and sorrow
only could be lit up with a lamp♪

00:15:34.130 --> 00:15:40.380 line:80%
♪Life passes in a blink♪

00:15:40.950 --> 00:15:44.610 line:80%
♪Years grow long,
yet simple joys grow few♪

00:15:44.610 --> 00:15:48.640 line:80%
♪Too many days lost♪

00:15:48.640 --> 00:15:52.830 line:80%
♪How many lovers♪

00:15:52.830 --> 00:15:56.400 line:80%
♪Once stood side by side
through hardships♪

00:15:56.400 --> 00:15:57.850 line:80%
♪In the end♪

00:15:59.780 --> 00:16:02.330 line:80%
I once promised Ning I'd protect you.

00:16:03.500 --> 00:16:05.050 line:80%
Never let you face this alone,

00:16:05.350 --> 00:16:06.290 line:80%
or let you seek revenge.

00:16:06.380 --> 00:16:08.100 line:80%
Now I'm afraid
I have to break that promise.

00:16:08.780 --> 00:16:09.620 line:80%
Zhao, rest assured.

00:16:10.900 --> 00:16:12.170 line:80%
I will avenge the Chang Fort.

00:16:12.860 --> 00:16:13.700 line:80%
Avenge my father.

00:16:14.740 --> 00:16:15.650 line:80%
Avenge myself.

00:16:17.570 --> 00:16:18.860 line:80%
Once I return to the Li Sect,

00:16:20.020 --> 00:16:21.260 line:80%
I will tear Nie Zhe

00:16:21.500 --> 00:16:22.810 line:80%
and the Demonic Camp

00:16:24.260 --> 00:16:25.570 line:80%
limb from limb.

00:16:26.880 --> 00:16:33.520 line:80%
♪For you, I guard the fading lamp♪

00:16:45.020 --> 00:16:45.860 line:80%
You didn't leave.

00:16:46.410 --> 00:16:47.650 line:80%
The Smiley spilled everywhere.

00:16:49.100 --> 00:16:50.140 line:80%
You owe me a new pouch.

00:16:50.860 --> 00:16:53.290 line:80%
The Snow Mountain is at least
a thousand li from here.

00:16:53.410 --> 00:16:55.650 line:80%
Even if you ride nonstop,
no food, no rest,

00:16:55.710 --> 00:16:57.140 line:80%
it'll take you dozens of days
to get there.

00:16:57.290 --> 00:16:58.690 line:80%
Why not take my Golden Peng?

00:16:59.020 --> 00:17:00.380 line:80%
You'll arrive in two days.

00:17:09.050 --> 00:17:09.980 line:80%
You rascal.

00:17:09.980 --> 00:17:10.940 line:80%
You're alive.

00:17:11.510 --> 00:17:12.450 line:80%
You were waiting for me.

00:17:12.810 --> 00:17:13.740 line:80%
How could I dare die?

00:17:41.020 --> 00:17:42.260 line:80%
Mr. Mu!

00:17:45.570 --> 00:17:46.410 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:17:46.570 --> 00:17:47.460 line:80%
This place of yours

00:17:47.570 --> 00:17:49.460 line:80%
was so hard for me to find.

00:17:49.550 --> 00:17:51.050 line:80%
If someone hadn't led the way outside,

00:17:51.180 --> 00:17:52.130 line:80%
I would have...

00:17:53.260 --> 00:17:56.500 line:80%
I would have never
seen you again, Mr. Mu.

00:17:57.220 --> 00:17:58.330 line:80%
My father loved peace,

00:17:58.940 --> 00:18:00.260 line:80%
hated being disturbed.

00:18:01.090 --> 00:18:03.530 line:80%
So he set up a Deadly Formation
outside the Carefree.

00:18:05.180 --> 00:18:06.330 line:80%
Does that mean I

00:18:06.500 --> 00:18:08.570 line:80%
can't gaze upon Mr. Mu's face every day,

00:18:08.570 --> 00:18:10.420 line:80%
and hear your teachings?

00:18:10.740 --> 00:18:13.260 line:80%
I can have someone teach you
how to break the formation.

00:18:13.700 --> 00:18:15.460 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Mu.

00:18:15.460 --> 00:18:16.570 line:80%
What have you found?

00:18:17.350 --> 00:18:19.180 line:80%
All altars and strongholds
are sealed off.

00:18:19.180 --> 00:18:20.050 line:80%
No one in, only out.

00:18:20.420 --> 00:18:22.500 line:80%
Fearing I'd alert the enemy

00:18:22.500 --> 00:18:23.740 line:80%
and ruin your grand plan, Mr. Mu,

00:18:23.850 --> 00:18:27.370 line:80%
I haven't found where the corpse slaves
are being forged yet.

00:18:29.290 --> 00:18:30.460 line:80%
Keep investigating.

00:18:32.700 --> 00:18:33.540 line:80%
Yes.

00:18:40.700 --> 00:18:41.540 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:18:42.130 --> 00:18:43.020 line:80%
Can he be trusted?

00:18:43.740 --> 00:18:45.370 line:80%
Trust doesn't matter.

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:48.220 line:80%
As long as he's useful to me.

00:19:02.940 --> 00:19:04.530 line:80%
(He hasn't killed Nie Zhe yet.)

00:19:04.710 --> 00:19:06.020 line:80%
(His vengeance remains unavenged.)

00:19:06.370 --> 00:19:07.530 line:80%
(So he surely won't die.)

00:19:07.530 --> 00:19:08.660 line:80%
Zhao!

00:19:09.810 --> 00:19:10.700 line:80%
Zhao.

00:19:12.220 --> 00:19:13.780 line:80%
I've found 30 shops.

00:19:13.980 --> 00:19:16.890 line:80%
Once the Golden Silk Soft Armor
hits the market, it'll stun the Jianghu.

00:19:17.170 --> 00:19:18.130 line:80%
It'll spread everywhere.

00:19:18.530 --> 00:19:20.810 line:80%
Good. With Xingjia handling it,
I'm at ease.

00:19:24.180 --> 00:19:25.020 line:80%
Zhao.

00:19:25.120 --> 00:19:26.810 line:80%
You've seemed troubled
these past few days.

00:19:33.660 --> 00:19:35.130 line:80%
I can't help but feel uneasy.

00:19:35.610 --> 00:19:36.850 line:80%
What makes you uneasy?

00:19:40.850 --> 00:19:42.530 line:80%
There was a fluffy little duckling.

00:19:43.980 --> 00:19:44.820 line:80%
Cute-looking.

00:19:45.190 --> 00:19:46.290 line:80%
But with a terrible temper.

00:19:46.810 --> 00:19:48.050 line:80%
After I raised it for a while,

00:19:48.720 --> 00:19:50.260 line:80%
I realized it wasn't a duckling at all.

00:19:51.020 --> 00:19:52.890 line:80%
It was a proud white goose.

00:19:53.850 --> 00:19:54.740 line:80%
Fine, it was a goose.

00:19:54.890 --> 00:19:56.660 line:80%
But he insists on
venturing into the world.

00:19:59.260 --> 00:20:00.530 line:80%
I'm a bit uneasy about it.

00:20:01.140 --> 00:20:02.530 line:80%
I fear he might get caught and roasted.

00:20:07.890 --> 00:20:08.730 line:80%
You...

00:20:09.030 --> 00:20:10.290 line:80%
Don't tell me you're eyeing Master Lei's

00:20:10.300 --> 00:20:11.500 line:80%
ducks.

00:20:11.980 --> 00:20:13.290 line:80%
Please, don't.

00:20:13.740 --> 00:20:15.130 line:80%
If you touch Master Lei's ducks,

00:20:15.130 --> 00:20:16.460 line:80%
he'll kill you.

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:27.300 line:80%
Zhao!

00:20:27.460 --> 00:20:28.850 line:80%
I'll buy you one tomorrow!

00:20:28.850 --> 00:20:30.330 line:80%
Don't do anything impulsive!

00:20:42.180 --> 00:20:43.020 line:80%
Hold out your hand.

00:20:45.940 --> 00:20:46.850 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:20:47.260 --> 00:20:48.780 line:80%
I've fully recovered already.

00:20:49.050 --> 00:20:50.850 line:80%
No need for any more
follow-ups now, right?

00:20:57.480 --> 00:20:58.500 line:80%
Who are you worried about?

00:21:00.810 --> 00:21:01.660 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:21:02.890 --> 00:21:04.260 line:80%
you're truly extraordinary.

00:21:05.020 --> 00:21:06.610 line:80%
I'm worried anyone could sense it.

00:21:07.180 --> 00:21:08.370 line:80%
Your pulse is thin and taut.

00:21:08.610 --> 00:21:09.850 line:80%
Dark circles beneath the eyes.

00:21:10.290 --> 00:21:11.460 line:80%
Restless through the night.

00:21:12.330 --> 00:21:13.460 line:80%
Too troubled to sleep.

00:21:15.070 --> 00:21:16.460 line:80%
You're worried about Chang Ning, right?

00:21:19.590 --> 00:21:21.570 line:80%
He's down the mountain
feasting and drinking richly.

00:21:21.890 --> 00:21:23.020 line:80%
Why should I worry about him?

00:21:23.130 --> 00:21:24.290 line:80%
Feasting and drinking richly.

00:21:25.190 --> 00:21:26.180 line:80%
That boy has a hard fate.

00:21:27.660 --> 00:21:29.940 line:80%
One day he might die somewhere,
with no one knowing.

00:21:31.260 --> 00:21:32.100 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:21:32.380 --> 00:21:33.570 line:80%
What do you mean "die somewhere"?

00:21:34.220 --> 00:21:35.180 line:80%
The poison in his body

00:21:35.420 --> 00:21:36.610 line:80%
wasn't completely removed.

00:21:36.690 --> 00:21:37.870 line:80%
But his martial arts and inner power

00:21:37.880 --> 00:21:39.050 line:80%
have all recovered, haven't they?

00:21:40.130 --> 00:21:40.980 line:80%
By reason,

00:21:42.120 --> 00:21:43.810 line:80%
the poison shouldn't be
severe now, right?

00:21:44.120 --> 00:21:45.100 line:80%
It's not that it isn't severe.

00:21:46.180 --> 00:21:47.050 line:80%
But it's quite severe.

00:21:49.020 --> 00:21:49.940 line:80%
Incurable.

00:22:01.090 --> 00:22:02.460 line:80%
He looked perfectly fine,

00:22:03.090 --> 00:22:04.780 line:80%
and fought harder than me.

00:22:10.980 --> 00:22:12.660 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:22:13.130 --> 00:22:15.570 line:80%
they say you're the greatest
Divine Healer in the world.

00:22:15.700 --> 00:22:16.980 line:80%
Isn't there any way

00:22:17.090 --> 00:22:18.290 line:80%
to cure his injury?

00:22:18.630 --> 00:22:21.260 line:80%
The impurities in his vital energy
and viscera have been drawn out,

00:22:21.980 --> 00:22:23.180 line:80%
but beneath the meridians,

00:22:23.810 --> 00:22:25.420 line:80%
a strange poison still lingers.

00:22:25.560 --> 00:22:26.850 line:80%
One I've never seen in my life.

00:22:26.860 --> 00:22:28.260 line:80%
Even with all my
acupuncture and medicine,

00:22:28.780 --> 00:22:29.660 line:80%
there's no cure.

00:22:30.530 --> 00:22:32.090 line:80%
I've warned him countless times before.

00:22:32.570 --> 00:22:34.330 line:80%
If one day he were gravely wounded,

00:22:34.570 --> 00:22:35.940 line:80%
or pushed his inner force too far,

00:22:37.130 --> 00:22:39.500 line:80%
his meridians might rupture
and claim his life.

00:22:41.660 --> 00:22:42.500 line:80%
That fool…

00:22:43.050 --> 00:22:44.290 line:80%
He's always trying to be tough.

00:22:44.780 --> 00:22:45.980 line:80%
Perhaps he himself

00:22:46.290 --> 00:22:47.660 line:80%
knows his days are numbered,

00:22:48.050 --> 00:22:49.420 line:80%
and he's set on revenge,

00:22:50.500 --> 00:22:51.740 line:80%
so he left alone and resolute.

00:22:52.230 --> 00:22:53.610 line:80%
You two were together day and night

00:22:54.980 --> 00:22:56.700 line:80%
and you never noticed anything?

00:22:57.500 --> 00:22:58.500 line:80%
I'll never let anyone

00:22:58.500 --> 00:22:59.890 line:80%
lock me up again.

00:23:00.330 --> 00:23:01.370 line:80%
Maybe it won't be long

00:23:02.370 --> 00:23:04.090 line:80%
before you're relieved of your worry.

00:23:07.700 --> 00:23:08.540 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:23:09.890 --> 00:23:11.090 line:80%
how much longer can he live?

00:23:11.090 --> 00:23:13.460 line:80%
He's barely sustained
by medicine right now.

00:23:14.570 --> 00:23:15.890 line:80%
Maybe a few years.

00:23:16.460 --> 00:23:17.530 line:80%
Maybe a few months.

00:23:18.180 --> 00:23:19.020 line:80%
I originally

00:23:19.330 --> 00:23:20.890 line:80%
prepared a medicinal incense for him

00:23:21.980 --> 00:23:22.890 line:80%
which could save his life

00:23:23.130 --> 00:23:24.050 line:80%
in a pinch.

00:23:26.420 --> 00:23:27.290 line:80%
It's a pity...

00:23:33.530 --> 00:23:34.370 line:80%
He's already gone.

00:23:34.380 --> 00:23:35.660 line:80%
You don't have to worry anymore.

00:23:37.270 --> 00:23:38.610 line:80%
Your master is entering seclusion again.

00:23:38.980 --> 00:23:40.370 line:80%
I've prepared some medicinal herbs.

00:23:41.020 --> 00:23:42.130 line:80%
Please help me deliver them.

00:23:47.420 --> 00:23:50.420 line:80%
(Chang Ning)

00:24:05.700 --> 00:24:07.620 line:80%
(Chang Ning)

00:24:17.460 --> 00:24:18.420 line:80%
By reason,

00:24:19.740 --> 00:24:21.130 line:80%
the poison shouldn't be
severe now, right?

00:24:21.420 --> 00:24:22.410 line:80%
It's not that it isn't severe.

00:24:23.220 --> 00:24:24.130 line:80%
But it's quite severe.

00:24:25.420 --> 00:24:26.260 line:80%
Incurable.

00:24:27.350 --> 00:24:29.420 line:80%
One day he might die somewhere,
with no one knowing.

00:24:30.180 --> 00:24:31.020 line:80%
Young Master said

00:24:31.420 --> 00:24:32.570 line:80%
he can't let you

00:24:32.570 --> 00:24:34.180 line:80%
be alone and helpless outside,

00:24:34.380 --> 00:24:36.850 line:80%
can't let you risk your life
at the Snow Mountain by yourself.

00:24:37.180 --> 00:24:38.660 line:80%
I am already a dying man.

00:24:39.520 --> 00:24:40.570 line:80%
If I live and can't avenge,

00:24:40.570 --> 00:24:41.660 line:80%
I might as well die.

00:24:42.260 --> 00:24:45.220 line:80%
(Chang Ning)

00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:17.850 line:80%
Just bring him some medicine.

00:25:17.980 --> 00:25:19.530 line:80%
I'll never expose my identity.

00:25:19.780 --> 00:25:21.180 line:80%
If he's missing
this life-saving medicine,

00:25:21.420 --> 00:25:22.940 line:80%
fails to avenge
and dies with regret,

00:25:23.140 --> 00:25:25.130 line:80%
that petty man will surely
become a vengeful ghost

00:25:25.370 --> 00:25:26.530 line:80%
and haunt me every day,

00:25:26.530 --> 00:25:27.660 line:80%
saying I'm ungrateful.

00:25:29.980 --> 00:25:30.940 line:80%
Zhao.

00:25:32.460 --> 00:25:33.420 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:25:34.850 --> 00:25:35.740 line:80%
It's getting late.

00:25:35.740 --> 00:25:37.130 line:80%
Whatever it is, let's talk tomorrow.

00:25:37.370 --> 00:25:38.260 line:80%
I need to rest now.

00:25:38.420 --> 00:25:39.920 line:80%
So you've truly made up your mind

00:25:39.930 --> 00:25:40.850 line:80%
to go to the demon sect?

00:26:02.820 --> 00:26:03.740 line:80%
Yuzhi, mind your words.

00:26:04.570 --> 00:26:06.290 line:80%
I'm a disciple of a righteous sect.

00:26:06.460 --> 00:26:08.020 line:80%
Why would I ever go to the demon sect?

00:26:08.460 --> 00:26:09.850 line:80%
You're going to find Chang Ning,

00:26:10.530 --> 00:26:12.130 line:80%
and Chang Ning is Mr. Mu.

00:26:12.130 --> 00:26:14.130 line:80%
You managed to get the saliva
so easily last time,

00:26:14.230 --> 00:26:16.290 line:80%
surely his help had something
to do with it, right?

00:26:16.780 --> 00:26:18.610 line:80%
Luoying Valley never forgets kindness.

00:26:18.610 --> 00:26:20.180 line:80%
If he were safe and sound,
it would be fine,

00:26:20.180 --> 00:26:21.700 line:80%
but now he's at death's door.

00:26:22.050 --> 00:26:23.660 line:80%
You must be going to repay his favor.

00:26:24.660 --> 00:26:25.660 line:80%
I suppose

00:26:25.660 --> 00:26:27.420 line:80%
you've even packed your things.

00:26:28.900 --> 00:26:29.860 line:80%
(Chang Ning)

00:26:36.660 --> 00:26:38.370 line:80%
Yuzhi, if you want to snitch on me,

00:26:39.500 --> 00:26:40.890 line:80%
then let's settle it with a duel.

00:26:43.660 --> 00:26:44.740 line:80%
I'm going with you.

00:26:45.520 --> 00:26:46.810 line:80%
Last time, I was healing,

00:26:46.810 --> 00:26:48.330 line:80%
forcing you to risk your life alone.

00:26:48.780 --> 00:26:50.090 line:80%
This time I ought to go with you,

00:26:50.090 --> 00:26:51.220 line:80%
to protect you.

00:26:51.370 --> 00:26:52.260 line:80%
Besides,

00:26:52.500 --> 00:26:55.090 line:80%
I need to borrow the Jade Sunflower
from Mr. Mu.

00:26:55.290 --> 00:26:56.330 line:80%
No, no.

00:26:56.810 --> 00:26:58.050 line:80%
If you go with me,

00:26:58.050 --> 00:26:59.660 line:80%
Lingbo will definitely hunt me down.

00:27:00.130 --> 00:27:01.890 line:80%
I'll get the Jade Sunflower for you.

00:27:01.890 --> 00:27:03.610 line:80%
Do you know how to
get to the Youming Path?

00:27:08.070 --> 00:27:10.290 line:80%
This is a route map I found
by looking through ancient texts.

00:27:13.500 --> 00:27:15.610 line:80%
It can help you avoid
many eerie caves along the way.

00:27:15.610 --> 00:27:16.850 line:80%
(Youming Path)
Straight to demon sect.

00:27:19.500 --> 00:27:20.460 line:80%
(Yichou)

00:27:20.660 --> 00:27:21.500 line:80%
Yichou?

00:27:22.460 --> 00:27:24.570 line:80%
This map is from sixteen years ago.

00:27:24.720 --> 00:27:25.700 line:80%
Can it still be accurate?

00:27:28.940 --> 00:27:30.020 line:80%
I'll cover all expenses.

00:27:34.130 --> 00:27:34.990 line:80%
No need.

00:27:34.990 --> 00:27:36.180 line:80%
I still have some savings of my own.

00:27:39.710 --> 00:27:41.980 line:80%
The defense of Qingque Sect
will also be my responsibility.

00:27:41.980 --> 00:27:43.020 line:80%
If I don't go with you,

00:27:43.020 --> 00:27:44.890 line:80%
you won't even
get past the Thousandfold Cliff.

00:27:45.500 --> 00:27:46.370 line:80%
Besides,

00:27:46.370 --> 00:27:47.220 line:80%
with me by your side,

00:27:47.220 --> 00:27:49.660 line:80%
you won't be accused of
colluding with the demon sect.

00:27:51.460 --> 00:27:52.700 line:80%
Then if I go with you,

00:27:53.850 --> 00:27:56.370 line:80%
I won't be accused of that?

00:27:56.410 --> 00:27:57.260 line:80%
You won't.

00:27:57.260 --> 00:27:58.100 line:80%
Why?

00:28:01.500 --> 00:28:02.340 line:80%
Right.

00:28:02.610 --> 00:28:03.570 line:80%
They'll only suspect me,

00:28:03.570 --> 00:28:04.940 line:80%
never you.

00:28:05.180 --> 00:28:06.850 line:80%
Comparing people
only breeds frustration.

00:28:08.780 --> 00:28:09.620 line:80%
No time to waste.

00:28:09.740 --> 00:28:10.660 line:80%
Let's set out now.

00:28:10.660 --> 00:28:12.660 line:80%
Milady, Yuzhi!

00:28:12.890 --> 00:28:15.370 line:80%
You can't elope!

00:28:17.660 --> 00:28:18.620 line:80%
(Lunar Gleam)
Elope?

00:28:18.940 --> 00:28:19.890 line:80%
Why would you elope?

00:28:19.890 --> 00:28:20.810 line:80%
Exactly.

00:28:21.090 --> 00:28:22.050 line:80%
Do I look that idle?

00:28:22.610 --> 00:28:23.500 line:80%
Milady.

00:28:23.850 --> 00:28:25.330 line:80%
If it's not eloping,

00:28:25.330 --> 00:28:27.790 line:80%
then why is a man and a woman
alone on a bed late at night,

00:28:27.800 --> 00:28:29.650 line:80%
plotting to go down the mountain?

00:28:29.890 --> 00:28:32.420 line:80%
Ning is in trouble down the mountain.

00:28:32.630 --> 00:28:34.570 line:80%
We're planning to go help him.

00:28:34.570 --> 00:28:36.330 line:80%
Then why not tell Master directly

00:28:36.330 --> 00:28:37.790 line:80%
and ask for his help?

00:28:38.610 --> 00:28:39.890 line:80%
Master's old wound hasn't healed.

00:28:40.120 --> 00:28:42.130 line:80%
Things on the mountain
have only just calmed down.

00:28:42.330 --> 00:28:43.980 line:80%
We don't want to trouble his mind.

00:28:44.940 --> 00:28:45.780 line:80%
Besides…

00:28:45.790 --> 00:28:47.980 line:80%
Chang Fort has shown great kindness
to our Luoying Valley.

00:28:49.740 --> 00:28:50.940 line:80%
How could we turn a blind eye?

00:28:51.090 --> 00:28:51.930 line:80%
Milady.

00:28:52.570 --> 00:28:53.850 line:80%
Go and come back quickly.

00:28:54.330 --> 00:28:55.170 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:28:55.530 --> 00:28:56.850 line:80%
I'll come back as soon as I'm done.

00:28:57.890 --> 00:28:59.510 line:80%
Wait, don't go yet.

00:29:02.460 --> 00:29:03.790 line:80%
Can you tell me the truth?

00:29:03.940 --> 00:29:05.580 line:80%
Are you heading to the demon sect?

00:29:11.090 --> 00:29:13.090 line:80%
Though the demon sect is in turmoil now,

00:29:13.260 --> 00:29:15.260 line:80%
it's still not easy to sneak in.

00:29:15.370 --> 00:29:16.660 line:80%
Go persuade Chang,

00:29:17.020 --> 00:29:18.940 line:80%
tell him not to be in such a hurry
to take revenge.

00:29:22.760 --> 00:29:24.600 line:80%
I'll pass on Xingjia's words

00:29:24.800 --> 00:29:26.090 line:80%
to Chang.

00:29:26.330 --> 00:29:27.890 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:29:28.020 --> 00:29:29.370 line:80%
you can set out with Zhao at ease.

00:29:29.450 --> 00:29:30.980 line:80%
Xiaolan and I will handle things here.

00:29:39.010 --> 00:29:39.940 line:80%
Zhao,

00:29:40.460 --> 00:29:41.630 line:80%
where are we going?

00:29:42.250 --> 00:29:44.330 line:80%
Hanhai Mountains are on the other side.

00:29:44.830 --> 00:29:46.050 line:80%
Come with me to meet someone first.

00:29:46.270 --> 00:29:47.610 line:80%
He must have the latest route map.

00:29:48.530 --> 00:29:49.370 line:80%
Alright.

00:29:57.330 --> 00:29:59.330 line:80%
The Young Master
ordered me to wait here,

00:30:00.020 --> 00:30:02.220 line:80%
so that Miss Cai wouldn't
venture into danger.

00:30:02.610 --> 00:30:05.610 line:80%
Hanhai Mountains are perilous now.

00:30:05.940 --> 00:30:09.050 line:80%
I cannot risk
handing over the route map.

00:30:09.080 --> 00:30:11.090 line:80%
Mu Qingyan already knows
I plan to descend the mountain?

00:30:13.530 --> 00:30:14.740 line:80%
How is he lately?

00:30:17.030 --> 00:30:18.660 line:80%
The Young Master
is masterminding everything.

00:30:18.660 --> 00:30:19.890 line:80%
He's doing fine.

00:30:21.090 --> 00:30:21.930 line:80%
Sir.

00:30:23.020 --> 00:30:24.940 line:80%
What's the current situation
in the Li Sect?

00:30:26.370 --> 00:30:27.420 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:30:27.780 --> 00:30:28.660 line:80%
Who is he?

00:30:29.260 --> 00:30:30.700 line:80%
This is my Third Senior Brother.

00:30:30.700 --> 00:30:31.540 line:80%
Song Yuzhi.

00:30:33.610 --> 00:30:34.530 line:80%
Mr. Pig?

00:30:36.090 --> 00:30:37.700 line:80%
Song Yuzhi, surname Song.

00:30:40.500 --> 00:30:43.050 line:80%
Everyone in the Li Sect
serves under the Young Master.

00:30:43.200 --> 00:30:44.330 line:80%
All is well there.

00:30:44.660 --> 00:30:45.800 line:80%
Mr. Pig.

00:30:46.220 --> 00:30:47.060 line:80%
Have some tea.

00:30:48.610 --> 00:30:49.530 line:80%
He's

00:30:49.530 --> 00:30:50.940 line:80%
Mr. Song.

00:30:51.740 --> 00:30:52.780 line:80%
The Hanhai Mountains

00:30:52.780 --> 00:30:53.850 line:80%
stretch for a thousand li.

00:30:53.850 --> 00:30:55.050 line:80%
Filled with countless traps.

00:30:55.050 --> 00:30:56.180 line:80%
Without a guide,

00:30:56.500 --> 00:30:58.980 line:80%
you'll never make it into the Li Sect.

00:30:59.610 --> 00:31:01.890 line:80%
Please leave after you finish your tea.

00:31:01.990 --> 00:31:04.020 line:80%
Mu Qingyan promised to
take responsibility for me.

00:31:04.180 --> 00:31:05.660 line:80%
Now he's turning his back on me?

00:31:07.050 --> 00:31:07.980 line:80%
Take...

00:31:07.980 --> 00:31:09.610 line:80%
Such a big matter.

00:31:09.810 --> 00:31:11.530 line:80%
I'm just a servant,
I can't make that call.

00:31:12.260 --> 00:31:14.180 line:80%
When the Young Master secures his place,

00:31:14.610 --> 00:31:16.610 line:80%
he will surely give you an explanation.

00:31:17.700 --> 00:31:18.700 line:80%
I has other business,

00:31:19.030 --> 00:31:20.050 line:80%
so I'll take my leave now.

00:31:33.340 --> 00:31:35.090 line:80%
Even making wontons
counts as taking responsibility.

00:31:35.180 --> 00:31:36.130 line:80%
I'm not lying.

00:31:41.020 --> 00:31:41.890 line:80%
Zhao.

00:31:41.890 --> 00:31:42.730 line:80%
Look.

00:31:44.570 --> 00:31:45.810 line:80%
Could it be a route map?

00:31:50.460 --> 00:31:51.700 line:80%
A safety talisman?

00:31:58.790 --> 00:32:00.090 line:80%
We can't just come here for nothing.

00:32:26.260 --> 00:32:27.220 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:32:27.940 --> 00:32:29.660 line:80%
You chose to come back
and die on your own.

00:32:29.980 --> 00:32:31.500 line:80%
Chief ordered us to fulfill your wish.

00:32:32.130 --> 00:32:33.050 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:32:33.050 --> 00:32:34.220 line:80%
Chief is merciful.

00:32:34.630 --> 00:32:35.530 line:80%
Why not

00:32:35.530 --> 00:32:37.290 line:80%
end the hostility and make peace?

00:32:37.420 --> 00:32:38.530 line:80%
Let's talk it over.

00:32:38.530 --> 00:32:39.370 line:80%
Master You,

00:32:40.460 --> 00:32:41.940 line:80%
you wanted to gaze upon my face,

00:32:42.460 --> 00:32:43.700 line:80%
and hear my teachings.

00:32:44.330 --> 00:32:45.500 line:80%
Why bring so many people here?

00:32:46.500 --> 00:32:47.570 line:80%
To listen together?

00:32:49.420 --> 00:32:50.260 line:80%
Master You,

00:32:50.520 --> 00:32:52.220 line:80%
I'll give you a chance
to redeem yourself.

00:32:52.570 --> 00:32:54.180 line:80%
Go take down that man named Mu.

00:32:54.740 --> 00:32:56.530 line:80%
I'll commend you to the strategist.

00:33:17.420 --> 00:33:18.290 line:80%
Kill him!

00:33:41.370 --> 00:33:42.210 line:80%
Go!

00:33:51.780 --> 00:33:53.220 line:80%
Master You, do you want to save Xing?

00:33:58.920 --> 00:34:09.580 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:34:28.340 --> 00:34:32.750 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:34:33.315 --> 00:34:37.930 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:34:38.270 --> 00:34:42.835 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:34:43.360 --> 00:34:47.660 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:34:50.605 --> 00:34:55.305 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:34:55.830 --> 00:35:00.120 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:35:00.780 --> 00:35:04.810 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:35:05.125 --> 00:35:10.250 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:35:10.825 --> 00:35:15.635 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:35:15.850 --> 00:35:20.020 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:35:20.745 --> 00:35:24.680 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:35:25.180 --> 00:35:30.455 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:35:53.185 --> 00:35:58.315 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:35:58.680 --> 00:36:03.050 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:36:03.315 --> 00:36:07.445 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:36:07.630 --> 00:36:13.205 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪